Package: causact
Type: Package
Title: Accelerated business analytics workflows
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Adam", "Fleischhacker", email = "ajf@udel.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Maintainer: Adam Fleischhacker <ajf@udel.edu>
Description: Causact is user friendly package disigned with the purpuse of facilitate the implementation of Bayesian
models. The packages uses a Directe Acyclic Graph (DAG) representation of the model that alows the user to easily 
understand relations between variables.    Causact is a graphical bridge between the matheatical and statistical
models and the user.
